	<p class="designerright">
		Originally from Hawthorne, New Jersey, Marjade Roniet is a womenswear
		designer and fashion practitioner. She is an MA Fashion Design
		graduate of Kingston University in London, England and a BFA Fashion
		Design graduate, of Syracuse University in New York. <br /> <br />
		Marjade has a particular interest in luxury and contemporary
		womenswear design. Her strengths include attention to detail, garment
		construction, research, creative problem-solving and visual
		communication. Marjade enjoys collaborations and working with clients
		to achieve quality design. She frequently finds inspiration through
		social observation. <br /> <br /> Although womenswear design is her
		primary focus, Marjade also has a background in menswear and
		childrenswear design. <br /> <br /> In addition to designing,
		Marjade's interests include dancing, traveling and playing
		instruments.
	</p>
